title: Jordyn Woods Backs That Thang Up Like a Boss on 22nd Birthday
text:
Jordyn Woods celebrated her first birthday without former best friend Kylie Jenner, but she has plenty of backside to cushion the blow.

The eyelash entrepreneur twerked her way through her 22nd birthday party with Jaden and Willow Smith on Monday.

Related Video: Kylie Jenner Opens Up About Falling Out With Jordyn Woods

Woods backed her juicy thang up in a revealing crochet pant displaying her thong bikini proudly.

With her hands on her knees for leverage, the birthday girl jiggled her booty for partygoers and it's pretty impressive.

View photos

Sporting a tiny black two-piece, the 22-year-old showed that her ex-bff was the furthest thing on her mind.

This is the first birthday Jordyn has spent without Kylie in years, but she had plenty of friends to celebrate with.

View photos

Besides Will Smith and Jada Pinkett Smith's super famous kids, Steve Harvey's daughter, Lori, and Instagram star Lexie Jayy was there to help Jordyn ring in the double digits.

View photos

They danced and sang, and also ate cake.

But it wasn't just any cake.
description: Jordyn Woods twerked her booty off on her 22nd birthday.
